results.description:
Paw prints left behind,
Bouncing towards joy ahead,
Rust streaks through white field.

This is the very first time Ellie saw mountains and snow. I think you can tell. I feel like her expression and elation at the discovery of this amazing thing in life quite accurately reflects my own inner feelings when in that environment. I guess animals are pretty good at showing us how awesome things around us can be at times.
Learn to let it show when you are madly in love with something, experience it to the extreme, then spend the night as tired out as if you ran a marathon.
